This program is implemented in python 3.7.

Current implementation is for demo purposes and has only been tested on MacBook Pro with display scale of 2880 * 1800

Steps

1. Install and run plant vs. zombie 1 (game of the year edition) from Origin
2. Set the screen's aspect to 1980 * 1080
3. Anchor the game window at the top left corner of the display
4. Start a new game, the current implementation only counts for levels before level 1-6
5. After 'ready, set, plant' passes, run the program, the current implementation terminates after running for 50 seconds.

Dependences:
    PIL
    numpy
    pyscreenshot
    opencv
    mss